<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Авторизация</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.2/css/font-awesome.min.css">

	<!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-1q8mTJOASx8j1Au+a5WDVnPi2lkFfwwEAa8hDDdjZlpLegxhjVME1fgjWPGmkzs7" crossorigin="anonymous">

	<!-- Optional theme -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" integrity="sha384-fLW2N01lMqjakBkx3l/M9EahuwpSfeNvV63J5ezn3uZzapT0u7EYsXMjQV+0En5r" crossorigin="anonymous">

	<script   src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.3.min.js"   integrity="sha256-a23g1Nt4dtEYOj7bR+vTu7+T8VP13humZFBJNIYoEJo="   crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-0mSbJDEHialfmuBBQP6A4Qrprq5OVfW37PRR3j5ELqxss1yVqOtnepnHVP9aJ7xS" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src = 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-3-typeahead/4.0.1/bootstrap3-typeahead.js'></script>
	<script src='./scripts/auth.js'></script>
</head>
<body>
<script>
	window.host = <%-JSON.stringify(host)%>;
</script>

<div class="container" style="width:600px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px">
	<h3>StudCloud.space - Панель администратора</h3>
</div>
<div class="container" style='width: 400px; margin-top: 30px;'>
	<div class="row" >
		<div class="col-lg-12">
			<br>
			<div class="alert alert-danger" style="visibility: hidden;">
				<span class="close" onclick='Auth.hideError();'>&times;</span>
				<strong>Ошибка входа</strong><br>
				Не распознана связка логин/пароль. Для восстановления доступа обратитеть к anzuev@istudentapp.ru
			</div>
			<form role="form">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="login">Логин</label>
					<input type="text" class="form-control" id="login" placeholder="Логин">
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="usersSearchFaculty">Пароль</label>
					<input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Пароль" autocomplete='off'>
				</div>
				<div class="btn btn-success pull-right " onclick='Auth.auth()'>Вход</div>
			</form>

		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>